snippet.textDisplay:
Regardless of what happens I still love Star Wars! That probably won’t change after I eventually see this movie. Not even the prequels changed that for me so I highly doubt this movie could be that bad.
My only fear is the new generations of kids who didn’t grow up with the original Star Wars or the prequels and don’t see what the big deal is! And after this trilogy is out they’ll probably be asking the same question. “What the big deal??”
If Disney’s goal was to bring back Star Wars for us to love again and for an new generation to admire the I’d say they have resoundingly FAILED to do that!
